338257b6625e5ff874abc9f5500a3f68","tid":2488657,"uid":287269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:39:18.000Z","msg":"「預防住院和死亡的有效率數據為100%」<br />\n<br />\n神父打完科興都要住院喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二人均完成接種兩劑科興疫苗，其中3月11日完成接種第2劑疫苗，相隔近一個月後，布拉科卻確診患上新冠肺炎。此外，該聲明續指，雖然二人感染症狀輕微，但仍需要使用特別醫療儀器照顧，以避免出現併發症。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2928905/%E6%89%93%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A9%E5%8A%91%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%8D%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%20%E6%99%BA%E5%88%A9%E4%B8%BB%E6%95%99%E7%95%99%E9%99%A2%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2928905%2F%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25AE%258C%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%258A%2591%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%2588%2588%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25BB%258D%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%2520%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%2588%25A9%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%2595%2599%25E7%2595%2599%25E9%2599%25A2%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25AF%259F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvjRqNRg6ChYs1Sy50pDDGUM%3D&h=2e4cfe03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2928905/%E6%89%93%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A9%E5%8A%91%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%8D%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%20%E6%99%BA%E5%88%A9%E4%B8%BB%E6%95%99%E7%95%99%E9%99%A2%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9F</a>"},{"pid":"be4b0dd526280619343e1b2010b7781f5ae282d1","tid":2488657,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:47:53.000Z","msg":"美国支持的，我们定必反对<br />\n🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳"}]}